<% unless unstarted.empty? %>
  <h2>Unstarted Trails</h2>
  <p>Warning: The JavaScript trail is basically a placeholder to prove to ourselves that we can do multiple trails simultaneously. It currently only has a single exercise in it. If you do the exercise we'll start you on the next one at that time.</p>
